verbose_text: Additionally to affecting the expression of the morning genes LHY / CCA1, PRR9, PRR7, PRR5, TOC1 negatively regulates the evening genes LUX (LUX ARRHYTHMO), ELF4 (EARLY FLOWERING 4) and GI (GIGANTEA) in the experimental data [XREF_BIBR] and in our model.
evidence: expression of the morning genes LHY/CCA1, PRR9, PRR7, PRR5
